# Always treat source files as text so a stray control byte (e.g. a NUL) can't make git
# misclassify a file as binary and hide its diff. `text` normalizes line endings to LF on
# commit; `diff` forces git to render a textual diff even if it heuristically looks binary.
*.ts     text diff
*.tsx    text diff
*.js     text diff
*.mjs    text diff
*.cjs    text diff
*.svelte text diff
*.json   text diff
*.css    text diff
*.html   text diff
*.md     text diff
